msg: Remove redundant NUM_TESTS array size and unused typedef.

author: jorton
msg: Don't link testdso.lo into testall as it hasn't been CuTestified yet.

author: jwoolley
msg: Fixed the apr_mmap_dup ownership problem for disjoint pools by getting
rid of the is_owner thing completely.  Instead, we place all of the dup'ed
apr_mmap_t's in a ring with each other (essentially the same as refcounting
the mmaped region but without the where-do-you-store-it pitfall).

author: rbb
msg: Change how individual test programs are run.  Now, testall is the driver
for all tests.  IF you just want to run individual tests, you do that
by passing the name of the test to testall.
